(15, '[Cakephp] Bài 4 – Tạo một Model – View – Controller', 'Ở bài trước chúng ta đã tìm hiểu vềỞ bài trước chúng ta đã tìm hiểu vềỞ bài trước chúng ta đã tìm hiểu vềỞ bài trước chúng ta đã tìm hiểu vềỞ bài trước chúng ta đã tìm hiểu vềỞ bài trước chúng ta đã tìm hiểu về', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">Ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ sử dụng lại database v&agrave; project&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">cakephp</strong>&nbsp;đ&atilde; tạo ra ở&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #337ab7; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="http://nongdanit.info/php-mysql/huong-dan-cai-dat-cakephp.html" target="_blank">B&agrave;i 2 &ndash; Hướng dẫn c&agrave;i đặt CakePHP</a></p>\r\n<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 20px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; color: #333333;">\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">T&ecirc;n database:&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">cakephp</strong></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">T&ecirc;n project:&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">cakephp</strong></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Link truy cập: http://localhost:8080/cakephp(<a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #337ab7; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="http://nongdanit.info/php-mysql/cach-doi-cong-va-su-dung-ten-mien-ao-localhost-xampp.html">đ&atilde; đổi port</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">B&acirc;y giờ trong database&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">cakephp</strong>, ta tiến h&agrave;nh tạo một table c&oacute; t&ecirc;n l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">users</strong>&nbsp;với c&aacute;c&nbsp;columns:</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #337ab7; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" title="" href="http://nongdanit.info/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2015-08-28_151356.png" data-rel="lightbox-0"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-445" style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; margin-bottom: 1.625em; border: 0px; clear: both; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://nongdanit.info/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2015-08-28_151356.png" alt="2015-08-28_151356" width="643" height="160" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">Khi ta c&oacute; một table&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">users</strong>, th&igrave; trong thư mục Model (C:\\xampppp\\htdocs\\cakephp\\app\\Model) ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ tạo một file&nbsp;User.php, với nội dung:</p>\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 20px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">\r\n<div id="highlighter_889753" class="syntaxhighlighter  php" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 780.531px; font-size: 1em !important; margin: 1em 0px !important; position: relative !important; overflow-x: auto !important; overflow-y: hidden !important;">\r\n<table style="font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; width: 780px; box-sizing: content-box !important; border: 0px !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; font-family: Monaco, Consolas, ''Bitstream Vera Sans Mono'', ''Courier New'', Courier, monospace !important; font-size: 1em !important; margin: 0px !important; outline: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; border-radius: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; direction: ltr !important; box-shadow: none !important; table-layout: auto !important; background: none !important;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody style="font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; box-sizing: content-box !important; border: 0px !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; font-size: 1em !important; margin: 0px !important