order-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#global-scopes">Global Scopes</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#relationships">Relationships</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#querying-relations">Querying Relations</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#eager-loading">Eager Loading</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#inserting-related-models">Inserting Related Models</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#touching-parent-timestamps">Touching Parent Timestamps</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#working-with-pivot-tables">Working With Pivot Tables</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#collections">Collections</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#accessors-and-mutators">Accessors &amp; Mutators</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#date-mutators">Date Mutators</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#attribute-casting">Attribute Casting</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#model-events">Model Events</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#model-observers">Model Observers</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#model-url-generation">Model URL Generation</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#converting-to-arrays-or-json">Converting To Arrays / JSON</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 15px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#introduction">Introduction</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The Eloquent ORM included with Laravel provides a beautiful, simple ActiveRecord implementation for working with your database. Each database table has a corresponding "Model" which is used to interact with that table.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Before getting started, be sure to configure a database connection in&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">config<span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">/</span>database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">.</span>php</code>.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="basic-usage"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#basic-usage">Basic Usage</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To get started, create an Eloquent model. Models typically live in the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">app</code>&nbsp;directory, but you are free to place them anywhere that can be auto-loaded according to your&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">composer<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">.</span>json</code>&nbsp;file. All Eloquent models extend&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Illuminate\\<span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Eloquent<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Model</span></code>.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining An Eloquent Model</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also generate Eloquent models using the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">make<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">:</span>model</code>&nbsp;command:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;">php artisan make<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">:</span>model User</code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Note that we did not tell Eloquent which table to use for our&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>&nbsp;model. The "snake case", plural name of the class will be used as the table name unless another name is explicitly specified. So, in this case, Eloquent will assume the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>&nbsp;model stores records in the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">users</code>&nbsp;table. You may specify a custom table by defining a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">table</code>&nbsp;property on your model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$table</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''my_users''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;Eloquent will also assume that each table has a primary key column named&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">id</code>. You may define a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">primaryKey</code>&nbsp;property to override this convention. Likewise, you may define a<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">connection</code>&nbsp;property to override the name of the database connection that should be used when utilizing the model.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Once a model is defined, you are ready to start retrieving and creating records in your table. Note that you will need to place&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated_at</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">created_at</code>&nbsp;columns on your table by default. If you do not wish to have these columns automatically maintained, set the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$timestamps</span></code>&nbsp;property on your model to&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token boolean" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">false</span></code>.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Retrieving All Records</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">all<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Retrieving A Record By Primary Key</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">var_dump<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">name</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;All methods available on the&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/queries">query builder</a>&nbsp;are also available when querying Eloquent models.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Retrieving A Model By Primary Key Or Throw An Exception</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to throw an exception if a model is not found. To do this, you may use the<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">firstOrFail</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">findOrFail<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">firstOrFail<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Doing this will let you catch the exception so you can log and display an error page as necessary. To catch the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">ModelNotFoundException</code>, add some logic to your&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">app<span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">/</span>Exceptions<span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">/</span>Handler<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">.</span>php</code>&nbsp;file.</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">use</span> <span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Illuminate<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Eloquent<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>ModelNotFoundException</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Handler</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">ExceptionHandler</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">render<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$request</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> Exception <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$e</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">if</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$e</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">instanceof</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">ModelNotFoundException</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n        <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n           <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> // Custom logic for model not found...\r\n</span>        <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">parent</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">render<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$request</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$e</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Querying Using Eloquent Models</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">take<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">10</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">var_dump<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">name</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eloquent Aggregates</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, you may also use the query builder aggregate functions.</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$count</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">count<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you are unable to generate the query you need via the fluent interface, feel free to use&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">whereRaw</code>:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">whereRaw<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''age &gt; ? and votes = 100''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">25</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Chunking Results</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you need to process a lot (thousands) of Eloquent records, using the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">chunk</code>&nbsp;command will allow you to do without eating all of your RAM:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">chunk<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">200</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span>    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The first argument passed to the method is the number of records you wish to receive per "chunk". The Closure passed as the second argument will be called for each chunk that is pulled from the database.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Specifying The Query Connection</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also specify which database connection should be used when running an Eloquent query. Simply use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">on</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">on<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''connection-name''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you are using&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/database#read-write-connections">read / write connections</a>, you may force the query to use the "write" connection with the following method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">onWriteConnection<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="mass-assignment"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#mass-assignment">Mass Assignment</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When creating a new model, you pass an array of attributes to the model constructor. These attributes are then assigned to the model via mass-assignment. This is convenient; however, can be a&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">serious</strong>&nbsp;security concern when blindly passing user input into a model. If user input is blindly passed into a model, the user is free to modify&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">any</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">all</strong>&nbsp;of the model''s attributes. For this reason, all Eloquent models protect against mass-assignment by default.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To get started, set the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">fillable</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">guarded</code>&nbsp;properties on your model.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining Fillable Attributes On A Model</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">fillable</code>&nbsp;property specifies which attributes should be mass-assignable. This can be set at the class or instance level.</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$fillable</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''first_name''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''last_name''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''email''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In this example, only the three listed attributes will be mass-assignable.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining Guarded Attributes On A Model</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The inverse of&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">fillable</code>&nbsp;is&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">guarded</code>, and serves as a "black-list" instead of a "white-list":</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$guarded</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''password''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;When using&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">guarded</code>, you should still never pass&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Input<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span></code>&nbsp;or any raw array of user controlled input into a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">save</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">update</code>&nbsp;method, as any column that is not guarded may be updated.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Blocking All Attributes From Mass Assignment</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In the example above, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">id</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">password</code>&nbsp;attributes may&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">not</strong>&nbsp;be mass assigned. All other attributes will be mass assignable. You may also block&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">all</strong>&nbsp;attributes from mass assignment using the guard property:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$guarded</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''*''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="insert-update-delete"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#insert-update-delete">Insert, Update, Delete</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To create a new record in the database from a model, simply create a new model instance and call the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">save</code>&nbsp;method.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Saving A New Model</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">name</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''John''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;Typically, your Eloquent models will have auto-incrementing keys. However, if you wish to specify your own keys, set the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">incrementing</code>&nbsp;property on your model to&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token boolean" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">false</span></code>.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">create</code>&nbsp;method to save a new model in a single line. The inserted model instance will be returned to you from the method. However, before doing so, you will need to specify either a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">fillable</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">guarded</code>&nbsp;attribute on the model, as all Eloquent models protect against mass-assignment.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">After saving or creating a new model that uses auto-incrementing IDs, you may retrieve the ID by accessing the object''s&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">id</code>&nbsp;attribute:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$insertedId</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">id</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Setting The Guarded Attributes On The Model</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$guarded</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''account_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Using The Model Create Method</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">// Create a new user in the database...\r\n</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">create<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''name''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''John''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">\r\n// Retrieve the user by the attributes, or create it if it doesn''t exist...\r\n</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">firstOrCreate<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''name''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''John''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">\r\n// Retrieve the user by the attributes, or instantiate a new instance...\r\n</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">firstOrNew<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''name''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''John''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Updating A Retrieved Model</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To update a model, you may retrieve it, change an attribute, and use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">save</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">email</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''john@foo.com''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Saving A Model And Relationships</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to save not only a model, but also all of its relationships. To do so, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">push</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">push<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also run updates as queries against a set of models:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$affectedRows</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">update<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''status''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;No model events are fired when updating a set of models via the Eloquent query builder.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Deleting An Existing Model</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To delete a model, simply call the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">delete</code>&nbsp;method on the instance:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">delete<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Deleting An Existing Model By Key</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">destroy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">destroy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">destroy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, you may also run a delete query on a set of models:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$affectedRows</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">delete<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Updating Only The Model''s Timestamps</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you wish to simply update the timestamps on a model, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">touch</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">touch<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="soft-deleting"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#soft-deleting">Soft Deleting</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When soft deleting a model, it is not actually removed from your database. Instead, a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">deleted_at</code>timestamp is set on the record. To enable soft deletes for a model, apply the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">SoftDeletes</code>&nbsp;to the model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">use</span> <span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Illuminate<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Eloquent<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>SoftDeletes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">use</span> <span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">SoftDeletes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$dates</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''deleted_at''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To add a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">deleted_at</code>&nbsp;column to your table, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">softDeletes</code>&nbsp;method from a migration:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$table</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">softDeletes<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now, when you call the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">delete</code>&nbsp;method on the model, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">deleted_at</code>&nbsp;column will be set to the current timestamp. When querying a model that uses soft deletes, the "deleted" models will not be included in query results.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Forcing Soft Deleted Models Into Results</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To force soft deleted models to appear in a result set, use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">withTrashed</code>&nbsp;method on the query:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">withTrashed<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''account_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">withTrashed</code>&nbsp;method may be used on a defined relationship:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">posts<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">withTrashed<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you wish to&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">only</strong>&nbsp;receive soft deleted models in your results, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">onlyTrashed</code>method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">onlyTrashed<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''account_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To restore a soft deleted model into an active state, use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">restore</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">restore<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">restore</code>&nbsp;method on a query:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">withTrashed<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''account_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">restore<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Like with&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">withTrashed</code>, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">restore</code>&nbsp;method may also be used on relationships:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">posts<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">restore<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you wish to truly remove a model from the database, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">forceDelete</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">forceDelete<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">forceDelete</code>&nbsp;method also works on relationships:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">posts<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">forceDelete<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To determine if a given model instance has been soft deleted, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">trashed</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">if</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">trashed<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n   <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="timestamps"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#timestamps">Timestamps</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">By default, Eloquent will maintain the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">created_at</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated_at</code>&nbsp;columns on your database table automatically. Simply add these&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">timestamp</code>&nbsp;columns to your table and Eloquent will take care of the rest. If you do not wish for Eloquent to maintain these columns, add the following property to your model:</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Disabling Auto Timestamps</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$table</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''users''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$timestamps</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token boolean" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">false</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Providing A Custom Timestamp Format</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you wish to customize the format of your timestamps, you may override the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">getDateFormat</code>method in your model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getDateFormat<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''U''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="query-scopes"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#query-scopes">Query Scopes</a></h2>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining A Query Scope</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Scopes allow you to easily re-use query logic in your models. To define a scope, simply prefix a model method with&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">scope</code>:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">scopePopular<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">scopeWomen<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">whereGender<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''W''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Utilizing A Query Scope</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">popular<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">women<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">orderBy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''created_at''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Dynamic Scopes</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to define a scope that accepts parameters. Just add your parameters to your scope function:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">scopeOfType<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$type</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">whereType<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$type</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Then pass the parameter into the scope call:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">ofType<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''member''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="global-scopes"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#global-scopes">Global Scopes</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to define a scope that applies to all queries performed on a model. In essence, this is how Eloquent''s own "soft delete" feature works. Global scopes are defined using a combination of PHP traits and an implementation of&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Illuminate\\<span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Eloquent<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>ScopeInterface</span></code>.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">First, let''s define a trait. For this example, we''ll use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">SoftDeletes</code>&nbsp;that ships with Laravel:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">trait</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">SoftDeletes</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">/**\r\n     * Boot the soft deleting trait for a model.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">static</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">bootSoftDeletes<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">static</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">addGlobalScope<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">SoftDeletingScope</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If an Eloquent model uses a trait that has a method matching the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">bootNameOfTrait</code>&nbsp;naming convention, that trait method will be called when the Eloquent model is booted, giving you an opportunity to register a global scope, or do anything else you want. A scope must implement<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">ScopeInterface</code>, which specifies two methods:&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">apply</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">remove</code>.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">apply</code>&nbsp;method receives an&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Illuminate\\<span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Eloquent<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Builder</span></code>&nbsp;query builder object and the<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Model</code>&nbsp;it''s applied to, and is responsible for adding any additional&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">where</code>&nbsp;clauses that the scope wishes to add. The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">remove</code>&nbsp;method also receives a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Builder</code>&nbsp;object and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Model</code>&nbsp;and is responsible for reversing the action taken by&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">apply</code>. In other words,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">remove</code>&nbsp;should remove the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">where</code>&nbsp;clause (or any other clause) that was added. So, for our&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">SoftDeletingScope</code>, the methods look something like this:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">/**\r\n * Apply the scope to a given Eloquent query builder.\r\n *\r\n * @param  \\Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Builder  $builder\r\n * @param  \\Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model  $model\r\n * @return void\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">apply<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span>Builder <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$builder</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> Model <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$builder</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">whereNull<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getQualifiedDeletedAtColumn<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">extend<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$builder</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">/**\r\n * Remove the scope from the given Eloquent query builder.\r\n *\r\n * @param  \\Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Builder  $builder\r\n * @param  \\Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model  $model\r\n * @return void\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">remove<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span>Builder <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$builder</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> Model <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$column</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getQualifiedDeletedAtColumn<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$builder</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getQuery<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">array</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">wheres</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$key</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$where</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> // If the where clause is a soft delete date constraint, we will remove it from\r\n</span>       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> // the query and reset the keys on the wheres. This allows this developer to\r\n</span>       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> // include deleted model in a relationship result set that is lazy loaded.\r\n</span>        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">if</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">isSoftDeleteConstraint<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$where</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$column</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n        <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n            <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">unset<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">wheres</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$key</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n            <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">wheres</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">array_values<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">wheres</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n        <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="relationships"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#relationships">Relationships</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, your database tables are probably related to one another. For example, a blog post may have many comments, or an order could be related to the user who placed it. Eloquent makes managing and working with these relationships easy. Laravel supports many types of relationships:</p>\r\n<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#one-to-one">One To One</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#one-to-many">One To Many</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#many-to-many">Many To Many</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#has-many-through">Has Many Through</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#polymorphic-relations">Polymorphic Relations</a></li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#many-to-many-polymorphic-relations">Many To Many Polymorphic Relations</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="one-to-one"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">One To One</h3>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining A One To One Relation</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">A one-to-one relationship is a very basic relation. For example, a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>&nbsp;model might have one<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Phone</code>. We can define this relation in Eloquent:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">phone<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasOne<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Phone''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The first argument passed to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">hasOne</code>&nbsp;method is the name of the related model. Once the relationship is defined, we may retrieve it using Eloquent''s&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#dynamic-properties">dynamic properties</a>:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$phone</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">phone</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The SQL performed by this statement will be as follows:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;">select <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">*</span> from users where id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span>\r\n\r\nselect <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">*</span> from phones where user_id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Take note that Eloquent assumes the foreign key of the relationship based on the model name. In this case,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Phone</code>&nbsp;model is assumed to use a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">user_id</code>&nbsp;foreign key. If you wish to override this convention, you may pass a second argument to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">hasOne</code>&nbsp;method. Furthermore, you may pass a third argument to the method to specify which local column that should be used for the association:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasOne<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Phone''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foreign_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasOne<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Phone''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foreign_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''local_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining The Inverse Of A Relation</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To define the inverse of the relationship on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Phone</code>&nbsp;model, we use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsTo</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Phone</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">user<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In the example above, Eloquent will look for a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">user_id</code>&nbsp;column on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">phones</code>&nbsp;table. If you would like to define a different foreign key column, you may pass it as the second argument to the<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsTo</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Phone</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">user<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''local_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Additionally, you pass a third parameter which specifies the name of the associated column on the parent table:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Phone</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">user<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''local_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''parent_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="one-to-many"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">One To Many</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">An example of a one-to-many relation is a blog post that "has many" comments. We can model this relation like so:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Post</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">comments<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Comment''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now we can access the post''s comments through the&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#dynamic-properties">dynamic property</a>:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comments</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">comments</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you need to add further constraints to which comments are retrieved, you may call the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">comments</code>method and continue chaining conditions:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comments</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">comments<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''title''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''=''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foo''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">first<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Again, you may override the conventional foreign key by passing a second argument to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">hasMany</code>method. And, like the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">hasOne</code>&nbsp;relation, the local column may also be specified:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Comment''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foreign_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Comment''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foreign_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''local_key''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining The Inverse Of A Relation</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To define the inverse of the relationship on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Comment</code>&nbsp;model, we use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsTo</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Comment</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Post''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="many-to-many"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Many To Many</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Many-to-many relations are a more complicated relationship type. An example of such a relationship is a user with many roles, where the roles are also shared by other users. For example, many users may have the role of "Admin". Three database tables are needed for this relationship:<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">users</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">roles</code>, and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">role_user</code>. The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">role_user</code>&nbsp;table is derived from the alphabetical order of the related model names, and should have&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">user_id</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">role_id</code>&nbsp;columns.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">We can define a many-to-many relation using the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsToMany</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Role''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now, we can retrieve the roles through the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>&nbsp;model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you would like to use an unconventional table name for your pivot table, you may pass it as the second argument to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsToMany</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Role''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''user_roles''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also override the conventional associated keys:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Role''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''user_roles''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''user_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foo_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, you may also define the inverse of the relationship on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Role</code>&nbsp;model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Role</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">users<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="has-many-through"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Has Many Through</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The "has many through" relation provides a convenient short-cut for accessing distant relations via an intermediate relation. For example, a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Country</code>&nbsp;model might have many&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>&nbsp;through a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>model. The tables for this relationship would look like this:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;">countries\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    name <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n\r\nusers\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    country_id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    name <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n\r\nposts\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    user_id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    title <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string</code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Even though the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">posts</code>&nbsp;table does not contain a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">country_id</code>&nbsp;column, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">hasManyThrough</code>&nbsp;relation will allow us to access a country''s posts via&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$country</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">posts</span></code>. Let''s define the relationship:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Country</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">posts<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasManyThrough<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Post''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you would like to manually specify the keys of the relationship, you may pass them as the third and fourth arguments to the method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Country</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">posts<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">hasManyThrough<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Post''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''country_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''user_id''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="polymorphic-relations"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Polymorphic Relations</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Polymorphic relations allow a model to belong to more than one other model, on a single association. For example, you might have a photo model that belongs to either a staff model or an order model. We would define this relation like so:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Photo</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">imageable<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">morphTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Staff</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">photos<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">morphMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Photo''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''imageable''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Order</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">photos<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">morphMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Photo''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''imageable''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Retrieving A Polymorphic Relation</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now, we can retrieve the photos for either a staff member or an order:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$staff</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Staff<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$staff</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">photos</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$photo</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n   <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Retrieving The Owner Of A Polymorphic Relation</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">However, the true "polymorphic" magic is when you access the staff or order from the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Photo</code>&nbsp;model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$photo</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Photo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$imageable</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$photo</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">imageable</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">imageable</code>&nbsp;relation on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Photo</code>&nbsp;model will return either a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Staff</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Order</code>&nbsp;instance, depending on which type of model owns the photo.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Polymorphic Relation Table Structure</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To help understand how this works, let''s explore the database structure for a polymorphic relation:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;">staff\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    name <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n\r\norders\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    price <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n\r\nphotos\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    path <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n    imageable_id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    imageable_type <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string</code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The key fields to notice here are the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">imageable_id</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">imageable_type</code>&nbsp;on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">photos</code>&nbsp;table. The ID will contain the ID value of, in this example, the owning staff or order, while the type will contain the class name of the owning model. This is what allows the ORM to determine which type of owning model to return when accessing the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">imageable</code>&nbsp;relation.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="many-to-many-polymorphic-relations"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Many To Many Polymorphic Relations</h3>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Polymorphic Many To Many Relation Table Structure</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In addition to traditional polymorphic relations, you may also specify many-to-many polymorphic relations. For example, a blog&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Video</code>&nbsp;model could share a polymorphic relation to a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Tag</code>model. First, let''s examine the table structure:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;">posts\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    name <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n\r\nvideos\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    name <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n\r\ntags\r\n    id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    name <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string\r\n\r\ntaggables\r\n    tag_id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    taggable_id <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> integer\r\n    taggable_type <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span> string</code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Next, we''re ready to setup the relationships on the model. The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Video</code>&nbsp;model will both have a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">morphToMany</code>&nbsp;relationship via a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">tags</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Post</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">tags<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">morphToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Tag''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''taggable''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Tag</code>&nbsp;model may define a method for each of its relationships:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Tag</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">posts<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">morphedByMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Post''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''taggable''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">videos<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">morphedByMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Video''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''taggable''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="querying-relations"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#querying-relations">Querying Relations</a></h2>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Querying Relations When Selecting</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When accessing the records for a model, you may wish to limit your results based on the existence of a relationship. For example, you wish to pull all blog posts that have at least one comment. To do so, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">has</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$posts</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">has<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''comments''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also specify an operator and a count:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$posts</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">has<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''comments''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''&gt;=''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Nested&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">has</code>&nbsp;statements may also be constructed using "dot" notation:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$posts</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">has<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''comments.votes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you need even more power, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">whereHas</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">orWhereHas</code>&nbsp;methods to put "where" conditions on your&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">has</code>&nbsp;queries:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$posts</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">whereHas<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''comments''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$q</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$q</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''content''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''like''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foo%''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="dynamic-properties"></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Dynamic Properties</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eloquent allows you to access your relations via dynamic properties. Eloquent will automatically load the relationship for you, and is even smart enough to know whether to call the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">get</code>&nbsp;(for one-to-many relationships) or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">first</code>&nbsp;(for one-to-one relationships) method. It will then be accessible via a dynamic property by the same name as the relation. For example, with the following model&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$phone</span></code>:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Phone</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">user<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\User''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$phone</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Phone<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Instead of echoing the user''s email like this:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">echo</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$phone</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">user<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">first<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">email</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">It may be shortened to simply:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">echo</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$phone</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">email</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;Relationships that return many results will return an instance of the<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Illuminate\\<span class="token package" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Database<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Eloquent<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">\\</span>Collection</span></code>&nbsp;class.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="eager-loading"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#eager-loading">Eager Loading</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eager loading exists to alleviate the N + 1 query problem. For example, consider a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Book</code>&nbsp;model that is related to&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Author</code>. The relationship is defined like so:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Book</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">author<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Author''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now, consider the following code:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Book<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">all<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$book</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">echo</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$book</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">author</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">name</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">This loop will execute 1 query to retrieve all of the books on the table, then another query for each book to retrieve the author. So, if we have 25 books, this loop would run 26 queries.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Thankfully, we can use eager loading to drastically reduce the number of queries. The relationships that should be eager loaded may be specified via the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">with</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Book<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">with<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''author''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$book</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">echo</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$book</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">author</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">name</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In the loop above, only two queries will be executed:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;">select <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">*</span> from books\r\n\r\nselect <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">*</span> from authors where id in <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">4</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">5</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">.</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">.</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">.</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Wise use of eager loading can drastically increase the performance of your application.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, you may eager load multiple relationships at one time:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$books</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Book<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">with<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''author''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''publisher''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may even eager load nested relationships:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$books</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Book<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">with<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''author.contacts''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In the example above, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">author</code>&nbsp;relationship will be eager loaded, and the author''s&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">contacts</code>relation will also be loaded.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eager Load Constraints</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to eager load a relationship, but also specify a condition for the eager load. Here''s an example:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">with<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''posts''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">where<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''title''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''like''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''%first%''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In this example, we''re eager loading the user''s posts, but only if the post''s title column contains the word "first".</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, eager loading Closures aren''t limited to "constraints". You may also apply orders:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">with<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''posts''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">orderBy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''created_at''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''desc''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Lazy Eager Loading</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">It is also possible to eagerly load related models directly from an already existing model collection. This may be useful when dynamically deciding whether to load related models or not, or in combination with caching.</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$books</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Book<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">all<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$books</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">load<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''author''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''publisher''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also pass a Closure to set constraints on the query:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$books</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">load<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''author''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$query</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">orderBy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''published_date''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''asc''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="inserting-related-models"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#inserting-related-models">Inserting Related Models</a></h2>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Attaching A Related Model</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You will often need to insert new related models. For example, you may wish to insert a new comment for a post. Instead of manually setting the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">post_id</code>&nbsp;foreign key on the model, you may insert the new comment from its parent&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>&nbsp;model directly:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comment</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Comment</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''message''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''A new comment.''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$post</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comment</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$post</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">comments<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comment</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In this example, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">post_id</code>&nbsp;field will automatically be set on the inserted comment.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you need to save multiple related models:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comments</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Comment</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''message''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''A new comment.''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Comment</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''message''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''Another comment.''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Comment</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''message''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''The latest comment.''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$post</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$post</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">comments<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">saveMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comments</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Associating Models (Belongs To)</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When updating a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsTo</code>&nbsp;relationship, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">associate</code>&nbsp;method. This method will set the foreign key on the child model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$account</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Account<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">10</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">account<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">associate<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$account</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 45px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Inserting Related Models (Many To Many)</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also insert related models when working with many-to-many relations. Let''s continue using our&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Role</code>&nbsp;models as examples. We can easily attach new roles to a user using the<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">attach</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Attaching Many To Many Models</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">attach<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also pass an array of attributes that should be stored on the pivot table for the relation:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">attach<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''expires''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$expires</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Of course, the opposite of&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">attach</code>&nbsp;is&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">detach</code>:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">detach<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Both&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">attach</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">detach</code>&nbsp;also take arrays of IDs as input:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">detach<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">attach<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''attribute1''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''value1''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Using Sync To Attach Many To Many Models</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">sync</code>&nbsp;method to attach related models. The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">sync</code>&nbsp;method accepts an array of IDs to place on the pivot table. After this operation is complete, only the IDs in the array will be on the intermediate table for the model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">sync<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">3</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Adding Pivot Data When Syncing</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may also associate other pivot table values with the given IDs:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">sync<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''expires''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token boolean" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">true</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to create a new related model and attach it in a single command. For this operation, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">save</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''name''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''Editor''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In this example, the new&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Role</code>&nbsp;model will be saved and attached to the user model. You may also pass an array of attributes to place on the joining table for this operation:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''expires''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$expires</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="touching-parent-timestamps"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#touching-parent-timestamps">Touching Parent Timestamps</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When a model&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">belongsTo</code>&nbsp;another model, such as a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Comment</code>&nbsp;which belongs to a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>, it is often helpful to update the parent''s timestamp when the child model is updated. For example, when a<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Comment</code>&nbsp;model is updated, you may want to automatically touch the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated_at</code>&nbsp;timestamp of the owning&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>. Eloquent makes it easy. Just add a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">touches</code>&nbsp;property containing the names of the relationships to the child model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Comment</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$touches</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''post''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">post<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsTo<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Post''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now, when you update a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Comment</code>, the owning&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Post</code>&nbsp;will have its&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated_at</code>&nbsp;column updated:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comment</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Comment<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comment</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">text</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''Edit to this comment!''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$comment</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">save<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="working-with-pivot-tables"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#working-with-pivot-tables">Working With Pivot Tables</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">As you have already learned, working with many-to-many relations requires the presence of an intermediate table. Eloquent provides some very helpful ways of interacting with this table. For example, let''s assume our&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">User</code>&nbsp;object has many&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Role</code>&nbsp;objects that it is related to. After accessing this relationship, we may access the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">pivot</code>&nbsp;table on the models:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">foreach</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">as</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">echo</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">pivot</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">created_at</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Notice that each&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Role</code>&nbsp;model we retrieve is automatically assigned a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">pivot</code>&nbsp;attribute. This attribute contains a model representing the intermediate table, and may be used as any other Eloquent model.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">By default, only the keys will be present on the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">pivot</code>&nbsp;object. If your pivot table contains extra attributes, you must specify them when defining the relationship:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Role''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">withPivot<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foo''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''bar''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">foo</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">bar</code>&nbsp;attributes will be accessible on our&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">pivot</code>&nbsp;object for the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Role</code>&nbsp;model.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you want your pivot table to have automatically maintained&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">created_at</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated_at</code>timestamps, use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">withTimestamps</code>&nbsp;method on the relationship definition:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">belongsToMany<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''App\\Role''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">withTimestamps<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Deleting Records On A Pivot Table</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To delete all records on the pivot table for a model, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">detach</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">detach<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Note that this operation does not delete records from the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">roles</code>&nbsp;table, but only from the pivot table.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Updating A Record On A Pivot Table</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may need to update your pivot table, but not detach it. If you wish to update your pivot table in place you may use&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updateExistingPivot</code>&nbsp;method like so:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">roles<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">updateExistingPivot<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roleId</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$attributes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining A Custom Pivot Model</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Laravel also allows you to define a custom Pivot model. To define a custom model, first create your own "Base" model class that extends&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Eloquent</code>. In your other Eloquent models, extend this custom base model instead of the default&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Eloquent</code>&nbsp;base. In your base model, add the following function that returns an instance of your custom Pivot model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">newPivot<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span>Model <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$parent</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">array</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$attributes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$table</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$exists</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">YourCustomPivot</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$parent</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$attributes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$table</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$exists</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="collections"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#collections">Collections</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">All multi-result sets returned by Eloquent, either via the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">get</code>&nbsp;method or a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">relationship</code>, will return a collection object. This object implements the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">IteratorAggregate</code>&nbsp;PHP interface so it can be iterated over like an array. However, this object also has a variety of other helpful methods for working with result sets.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Checking If A Collection Contains A Key</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">For example, we may determine if a result set contains a given primary key using the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">contains</code>method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">if</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">contains<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n   <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Collections may also be converted to an array or JSON:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">toArray<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">toJson<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If a collection is cast to a string, it will be returned as JSON:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span>string<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Iterating Collections</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eloquent collections also contain a few helpful methods for looping and filtering the items they contain:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">each<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n   <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Filtering Collections</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When filtering collections, the callback provided will be used as callback for&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="http://php.net/manual/en/function.array-filter.php">array_filter</a>.</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$users</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">filter<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">isAdmin<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 3px; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: #f4645f;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0px; font-size: 14.5px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">Note:</strong>&nbsp;When filtering a collection and converting it to JSON, try calling the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">values</code>&nbsp;function first to reset the array''s keys.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Applying A Callback To Each Collection Object</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">roles</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">each<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n   <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sorting A Collection By A Value</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">sortBy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">created_at</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">sortByDesc<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$role</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">created_at</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sorting A Collection By A Value</h4>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">sortBy<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''created_at''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$roles</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">sortByDesc<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''created_at''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Returning A Custom Collection Type</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes, you may wish to return a custom Collection object with your own added methods. You may specify this on your Eloquent model by overriding the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">newCollection</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">newCollection<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">array</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$models</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">CustomCollection</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$models</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="accessors-and-mutators"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#accessors-and-mutators">Accessors &amp; Mutators</a></h2>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining An Accessor</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eloquent provides a convenient way to transform your model attributes when getting or setting them. Simply define a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">getFooAttribute</code>&nbsp;method on your model to declare an accessor. Keep in mind that the methods should follow camel-casing, even though your database columns are snake-case:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getFirstNameAttribute<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$value</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">ucfirst<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$value</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In the example above, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">first_name</code>&nbsp;column has an accessor. Note that the value of the attribute is passed to the accessor.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Defining A Mutator</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Mutators are declared in a similar fashion:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">User</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">extends</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Model</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">setFirstNameAttribute<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$value</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n        <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">attributes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''first_name''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">strtolower<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$value</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="date-mutators"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#date-mutators">Date Mutators</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">By default, Eloquent will convert the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">created_at</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated_at</code>&nbsp;columns to instances of&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; background-color: transparent;" href="https://github.com/briannesbitt/Carbon">Carbon</a>, which provides an assortment of helpful methods, and extends the native PHP&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">DateTime</code>&nbsp;class.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may customize which fields are automatically mutated, and even completely disable this mutation, by overriding the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">getDates</code>&nbsp;method of the model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getDates<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''created_at''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When a column is considered a date, you may set its value to a UNIX timestamp, date string (<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Y<span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span>m<span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span>d</code>), date-time string, and of course a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">DateTime</code>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">Carbon</code>&nbsp;instance.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To totally disable date mutations, simply return an empty array from the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">getDates</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getDates<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="attribute-casting"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#attribute-casting">Attribute Casting</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If you have some attributes that you want to always convert to another data-type, you may add the attribute to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">casts</code>&nbsp;property of your model. Otherwise, you will have to define a mutator for each of the attributes, which can be time consuming. Here is an example of using the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">casts</code>&nbsp;property:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">/**\r\n * The attributes that should be casted to native types.\r\n *\r\n * @var array\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$casts</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span>\r\n    <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''is_admin''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''boolean''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">is_admin</code>&nbsp;attribute will always be cast to a boolean when you access it, even if the underlying value is stored in the database as an integer. Other supported cast types are:&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">integer</code>,<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">real</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">float</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">double</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">string</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">boolean</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">object</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">array</span></code>.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">The&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">array</span></code>&nbsp;cast is particularly useful for working with columns that are stored as serialized JSON. For example, if your database has a TEXT type field that contains serialized JSON, adding the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">array</span></code>cast to that attribute will automatically deserialize the attribute to a PHP array when you access it on your Eloquent model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">/**\r\n * The attributes that should be casted to native types.\r\n *\r\n * @var array\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">protected</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$casts</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span>\r\n    <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''options''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''array''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Now, when you utilize the Eloquent model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">\r\n// $options is an array...\r\n</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$options</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">options</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">\r\n// options is automatically serialized back to JSON...\r\n</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">options</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''foo''</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''bar''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="model-events"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#model-events">Model Events</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Eloquent models fire several events, allowing you to hook into various points in the model''s lifecycle using the following methods:&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">creating</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">created</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updating</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">saving</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">saved</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">deleting</code>,<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">deleted</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">restoring</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">restored</code>.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Whenever a new item is saved for the first time, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">creating</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">created</code>&nbsp;events will fire. If an item is not new and the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">save</code>&nbsp;method is called, the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updating</code>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updated</code>&nbsp;events will fire. In both cases, the<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">saving</code>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">saved</code>&nbsp;events will fire.</p>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Cancelling Save Operations Via Events</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">If&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token boolean" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">false</span></code>&nbsp;is returned from the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">creating</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updating</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">saving</code>, or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">deleting</code>&nbsp;events, the action will be cancelled:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">creating<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">if</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">!</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">isValid<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token boolean" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">false</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Where To Register Event Listeners</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Your&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">EventServiceProvider</code>&nbsp;serves as a convenient place to register your model event bindings. For example:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true">/**\r\n * Register any other events for your application.\r\n *\r\n * @param  \\Illuminate\\Contracts\\Events\\Dispatcher  $events\r\n * @return void\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">boot<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span>DispatcherContract <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$events</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">parent</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">boot<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$events</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">creating<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span>    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="model-observers"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#model-observers">Model Observers</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To consolidate the handling of model events, you may register a model observer. An observer class may have methods that correspond to the various model events. For example,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">creating</code>,&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">updating</code>,<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">saving</code>&nbsp;methods may be on an observer, in addition to any other model event name.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">So, for example, a model observer might look like this:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">class</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">UserObserver</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">saving<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span>    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">saved<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$model</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n       <span class="token comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;" spellcheck="true"> //\r\n</span>    <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">You may register an observer instance using the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">observe</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">observe<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">new</span> <span class="token class-name" style="box-sizing: border-box;">UserObserver</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="model-url-generation"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#model-url-generation">Model URL Generation</a></h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When you pass a model to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">route</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">action</code>&nbsp;methods, it''s primary key is inserted into the generated URI. For example:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Route<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''user/{user}''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''UserController@show''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">action<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''UserController@show''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">In this example the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">id</span></code>&nbsp;property will be inserted into the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;"><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>user<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code>&nbsp;place-holder of the generated URL. However, if you would like to use another property instead of the ID, you may override the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">getRouteKey</code>&nbsp;method on your model:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">public</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getRouteKey<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">slug</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #f4645f; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;" name="converting-to-arrays-or-json"></a></p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 55px; position: relative; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #525252; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" href="https://laravel.com/docs/5.0/eloquent#converting-to-arrays-or-json">Converting To Arrays / JSON</a></h2>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Converting A Model To An Array</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">When building JSON APIs, you may often need to convert your models and relationships to arrays or JSON. So, Eloquent includes methods for doing so. To convert a model and its loaded relationship to an array, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">toArray</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">=</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">with<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''roles''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">first<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4ea1df;">$user</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">toArray<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Note that entire collections of models may also be converted to arrays:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">all<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">toArray<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Converting A Model To JSON</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">To convert a model to JSON, you may use the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: #f0f2f1;">toJson</code>&nbsp;method:</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">find<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token number" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">toJson<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Returning A Model From A Route</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Note that when a model or collection is cast to a string, it will be converted to JSON, meaning you can return Eloquent objects directly from your application''s routes!</p>\r\n<pre class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle; background: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.34902);"><code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">Route<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">get<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''users''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">,</span> <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">User<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">::</span></span><span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">all<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span></code></pre>\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 35px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Hiding Attributes From Array Or JSON Conversion</h4>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Sometimes you may wish to limit the attributes that are included in your model''s array or JSON form, such as passwords. To do so, add a&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 2; tab-size: 4; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.121569) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-