border-box; color: #0077aa;">function</span> <span class="token function" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">getIsAdminAttribute<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">(</span></span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">)</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">{</span>\r\n    <span class="token keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0077aa;">return</span> <span class="token this" style="box-sizing: border-box;">$this</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">-</span><span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">&gt;</span><span class="token property" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #da564a;">attributes</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">[</span><span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''admin''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">]</span> <span class="token operator" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555;">==</span> <span class="token string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #2e7d32;">''yes''</span><span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">;</span>\r\n<span class="token punctuation" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999999;">}</span></code></pre>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.7; margin: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 14.5px; color: #525252; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', sans-serif;">Once you have created the accessor, just add the value to the&nbsp;<code class=" language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Andale Mono'', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #f4645f; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: 